result_quotes: "Yeah, like in the last two years, I've probably had two or three viral infections, just just just cold cold symptoms."
"Um, I do feel sometimes I get like more tired than I used to throughout the day."
"Yeah, that and I just start coughing so much that I just have to sit down."
"Not weakness, I'll just say more fatigue."
"I was a bit worried because I've been having this cough for around two years, which has been getting worse. But recently I've noticed that I see streaks of blood in the sputum that I'm producing."
"Any joint pains or or muscle pains?"
"Sometimes I would say like when when, it gets worse when I'm exerting myself more, I I can get some wheezing."
"No, I'm pretty fine during the night."
